    "In comparison, ChatSim has multiple collaborative agents with specific roles, ensuring accurate task execution.",
    "3D detection with simulation data.",
    "We validate the benefits of our simulation as data augmentation for a downstream 3D object detection task on Waymo Open Dataset [61].",
    "We simulate 1960 frames, derived from scenes in the training dataset.In the simulation, cars with various types, locations, and orientations are incorporated.",
    "The detection model adopts Lift-Splat [54]."
